						<p><hi rend="bold">Śaka 1471 (1549 A.D.)</hi></p>						

						<p>Incomplete. Contains the date Śaka 1471, Saumya, Vriśchika, corres ponding to 1549 A.D., November. The details of date, viz. <hi rend="italic">tithi</hi> 7, Saturday and Uttiraṭṭādi are irregular. Seems to refer to some endowment made into the <hi rend="italic">Śrībhaṇḍāram</hi> of the temple.</p>						

